cs.OS, cs.EM, cs.RT, cs.SY, cs.PL 

The paper discusses scheduling algorithms for mixed-criticality systems, which typically fall under the categories of operating systems (cs.OS), embedded systems (cs.EM), real-time systems (cs.RT), systems and control (cs.SY), and programming languages (cs.PL). The focus on demand-based schedulability tests and deadline tightening strategies further supports these categories.
